:::Starscream:::

::His mouth drops when Destructor is killed.  That was the quickest and 
simplest death he had seen since his own.  He tried to keep from smiling to 
himself; now that Destructor was dead, his only competition for Kitkat would 
be Drillbit. If he could just- No! he thought to himself, you have to stop 
thinking that! he had decided long ago that he wouldnt come between them, and 
he was keeping that promise . . . for now::

--part1_a8.d483520.274afff3_boundary
